Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,THE BLACK CORE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you're ready for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Howl, {\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Vortex Axe!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.41,0:02:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall be your opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.78,0:02:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think you'll beat me that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.37,0:03:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the power of the Dragonoid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,A truly worthy opponent indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You still don't seem to understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dragonoid does not stop\Nuntil its opponent is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.51,0:04:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the ultimate battle form\Nof a Dragon Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I have taken this form,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.94,0:04:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you stand no chance\Nno matter how hard you try!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.07,0:04:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you can't use your sword\Nor Extreme Spells for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's strong... Too strong!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This Superior Being body was created\Nbased on the Dragonoid's abilities!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It should rival or even surpass Baran!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:04:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why can't I do anything to him?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He's powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Hadorra is powerless against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like Hadorra\Ndisturbed the beast's nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Every animal lashes out\Nif its nest is disturbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They display extraordinary strength\Nto protect their young.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And unleash harsh punishment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the same.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose that settles it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to detonate the Black Core?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that Hadorra cannot win,\Nthis is only mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.37,0:05:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All I do is emit my Magic Power\Nfrom this finger and the Core explodes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:06:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,When Baran comes in contact with Hadorra...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,that's when everything ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You would still fight, Hadorra?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're trying to use\NUltra Combustion Slash with a broken arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pure futility!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what you will!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Simply waiting to die on the ground\Nwould be worse than this pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,At the very least, I can try!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I accept your challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,How disappointing it is, Baran.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.13,0:08:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,To come so far yet come up short.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Your final effort\Nwas most impressive, Hadorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But fear not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.69,0:08:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,As you hoped, even in death\Nyou can still defeat Baran.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Here at this very moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Shatter into pieces, Black Core!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.58,0:08:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I emitted my Magic Power, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why doesn't the Core explode?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:09:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You underestimated me, Dark King Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.98,0:09:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I accepted Hadorra's final challenge?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It was because\NI was waiting for this chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So I could prevent the Black Core's\Nexplosion with my Dragonic Aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, Baran.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.59,0:09:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So he was prepared for the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.59,0:09:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.77,0:09:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that thing doing inside of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,As a Darkling, you must have heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.39,0:09:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a Black Core!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.36,0:09:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A Black Core?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.52,0:09:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.33,0:10:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The cursed legendary explosive\Nwas inside of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?! Who would do such a thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.71,0:10:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Who else?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.42,0:10:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It was your master.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who promised you\Nthe surface world,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.55,0:10:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,while ruthlessly intending\Nto destroy it anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.88,0:10:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,King Ban?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I see now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.43,0:10:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You and Dai were holding back\Nbecause of the Black Core!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to a fair fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no way you could have won\Nunder such conditions!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I sacrificed my own body...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.79,0:10:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I sacrificed my own life\Nto have this battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hadorra...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:11:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my. How pathetic, Hadorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.88,0:11:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped, Kilban.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect the power of Baran's Aura\Nas a Dragonoid to be this strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.89,0:11:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He repelled my Magic Power.\NHow very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But as the Core's creator,\Nall I need to do is approach it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.08,0:11:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and detonating it should be no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall go myself\Nand erase them along with the Core.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,King Ban, if you go out there,\Nit'll just put us to shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Myst?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And there he goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.74,0:11:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm removing the Core from you\Nbefore Ban makes his next move!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystban?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here to eliminate us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystban...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you share King Ban's opinion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you here to discard me\Nlike a useless tool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Was I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.85,0:12:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Was I just a pawn to you, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I have but one answer to your question.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark King's words\Ntake precedence above all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So that's your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're already too late, Mystban.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with you here I can't be defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.89,0:13:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I can erase the both of you\Nwithout even a touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this powerful tremor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,King Ban, do I have your permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I grant it, Mystban.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:06.53,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}ULTRA COMBUSTION SLASH{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:11.53,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}GIGABRAKE{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystban's true form?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,With the flash of the Black Core, begone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The Core has been activated?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.43,0:14:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Impossible!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My Dragonoid Dragonic Aura\Nshould repel any Magic Power!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.02,0:14:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It would take Ban's own\NMagic Power at close proximity to...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Detonate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:15:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the Magic Power of\Na Black Core's creator can detonate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystban! Does this mean\Nyour real form...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.63,0:15:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,In a moment, you two\Nwill be erased from this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.85,0:15:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you have seen this face,\Nyou cannot be allowed to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this strange rumbling?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure,\Nbut I have a bad feeling about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.42,0:15:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Where are you facing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody! Gather in one place!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.27,0:16:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's happening\Nto the Field of Death!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?! Meruru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.74,0:16:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A white flash is swallowing everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.54,0:16:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is going to vanish!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.25,0:16:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.59,0:16:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.17,0:16:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it connected to this rumbling?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess! Emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The Field of Death\Nhas suddenly begun shaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like... an active volcano!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something happening again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We must go save the Heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.57,0:16:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.32,0:16:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Who...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! You're alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We must leave this place immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.29,0:17:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.38,0:17:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's no good! The explosion is inevitable!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye Hadorra. And Baran.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.90,0:17:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The two men King Ban himself respected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.52,0:17:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Your names shall be etched in my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.74,0:17:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.57,0:18:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.07,0:18:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So Ban Palace is finally going to move?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're covering up already?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.89,0:18:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Your true face is so much cooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.14,0:18:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So much cooler!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.64,0:18:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That power should not be unduly exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,As you command, my Dark King.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done well, Mystban.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.77,0:18:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.03,0:18:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,All of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hero, Baran and all other nuisances\Nhave all been erased...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,along with the Field of Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.25,0:19:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're all that's left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.87,0:19:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Us...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.75,0:19:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and Ban Palace itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now it is time for\Nthe surface world to be erased.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm removing the barrier\Naround Ban Palace now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.77,0:19:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The remaining rocks that covered it\Nshould all fall away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,However, too much remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.11,0:19:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,With the explosion of the Black Core,\Naside from Ban Palace,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.87,0:19:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,all the rocks should have been\Nreduced to ash.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.12,0:19:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystban, have the Heyedras\Nsearch for any survivors.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.55,0:19:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My King!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.64,0:20:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Survivors! Survivors spotted!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.77,0:20:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Four survivors on the left wing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.27,0:20:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The Disciples of Aban.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.07,0:20:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They survived? In that explosion?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.07,0:20:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How very fortunate of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.25,0:20:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That explosion was unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.59,0:20:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Who saved us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.38,0:20:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It was probably Big Guy here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Who else has the strength to save us\Nby burying us all alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.68,0:20:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop complaining.\NAt least we're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.89,0:20:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured that underground\Nwas probably the safest place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So I dug a hole in the ground\Nbig enough to hide us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.69,0:20:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea. It was probably\Nthe only option given that blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.77,0:21:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The Royal Guard are all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.15,0:21:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like we're\Nthe only ones who survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.74,0:21:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice judgment call!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.25,0:21:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.29,0:21:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.34,0:21:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is nothing like\Nthe Field of Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.75,0:21:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is probably Ban Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The explosion tore away the Field of Death\Nand exposed what lied beneath.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.22,0:21:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that thing way over there is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.76,0:21:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be Dark King Ban's palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.85,0:21:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.06,0:21:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.32,0:21:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're saying we just flew into the sky\Nwith Ban Palace?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.26,0:22:12.14,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}omoeba boku wa bukiyou de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.26,0:22:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To be honest I was clumsy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.31,0:22:18.48,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shouganaikurai tomawarishita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.31,0:22:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it took me forever to get here{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.98,0:22:23.94,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kodokukannsura mo buki ni shite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.98,0:22:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I used even loneliness as a weapon{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.11,0:22:29.87,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tannjun na kotae wo sagashita dannjon{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.11,0:22:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I searched the dungeon for a simple answer{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.03,0:22:35.70,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tadashisa yasashisa nagedashite mo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.03,0:22:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I cast aside\NRightness and kindness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.87,0:22:41.84,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitori kimi no mikata de itai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.87,0:22:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just want to be there for you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.00,0:22:47.47,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu koto ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.00,0:22:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.63,0:22:53.47,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ari to arayuru mahou yori muzukashikute{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.63,0:22:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is harder than any magic spell{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.64,0:22:59.27,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}konnani mo chikaku ni itanoni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.64,0:22:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though you're so close to me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.44,0:23:01.90,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}aishiteiru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.44,0:23:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.06,0:23:05.19,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}imasara kizuitanosa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.06,0:23:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I finally realized it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.36,0:23:10.32,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu tame ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.36,0:23:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.49,0:23:16.75,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku wa kitto umarete kitannda{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.49,0:23:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Must be the reason I was born{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.91,0:23:22.67,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shigamitsuku yoru furihodoite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.91,0:23:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shake off the clinging night{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.84,0:23:25.38,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni iku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.84,0:23:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And go to see you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.55,0:23:30.13,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima sugu kimi no moto e{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.55,0:23:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now to where you are{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.05,0:23:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Black Core erased the Field of Death\Nand exposed Ban Palace's true form.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.81,0:23:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Popp and the others who survived\Nquickly go to find Dai,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.15,0:23:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but find the horrifying results\Nof Baran and Hadorra's fight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.07,0:23:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dark King Ban makes\Nhis merciless next move against them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.03,0:23:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.41,0:23:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Inherited Heart"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.25,0:24:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
